README
======

Starbug PHP pre-release alpha

What is Starbug PHP?
----------------

Starbug is a full featured PHP web application framework that employs a Model-View design
pattern. It is modeled around the HTTP Protocol and has a small footprint.


Design Principles
----------------

Starbug PHP was designed to be a small and efficient codebase that is highly
extensible.

Requirements
------------

Starbug PHP requires PHP 5 with the PDO extension. Using the code generator
requires Saxon XSLT processor.

Documentation
-------------

http://www.starbugphp.com/documentation
